title: One bedroom with tons of storage and Updates!
posting_body: ['APARTMENT INFO:', '-----------------------------------------------', '- Large windows', '- Multiple updates throughout', '- Built-In A/C', '- SO MANY CLOSETS', '- USI Ready!', 'Check out the photos and video tour of a similar unit:', 'https://youtu.be/LP4BYxTe6mA', 'LOCATION INFO:', '--------------------------------------------------------------', '2536 Lyndale Ave is a fantastic location in Uptown, just a short distance from some great eateries in the area.', 'The Bulldog, French Meadow, Common Roots, and all the restaurants of Eat Street are all walking distance.', 'There is also private parking available on site that ensures you always have a spot to park your car.', 'Within the unit there is a wall A/C unit that will keep you cool in the summer months.', 'LEASING INFO', '---------------------------------------', '$40 application fee', '$1145 deposit', '$1145 monthly rent', 'Parking Available for $65/mo-', 'Read about our rental criteria and apply here at the Irving Properties website: <URL>', 'This is a pet free and smoke free building', 'UTILITIES', '---------------------------------------', 'Residents pay electricity, water, and optional cable/internet', 'Management pays trash, sewer and heat.', 'Call or email IrvingProperties to schedule your showing:', 'Be sure to check out application on line and qualifications and requirements', '<URL>']
